  The 2014 summit will be held at the <b>MIT Media Lab (E14)</b>, 75 Amherst Street, Cambridge, MA 02139 USA. The venue is <b>public transit accessible</b> and located within a 5-minute walk of the Kendall/MIT station on the MBTA Red Line.<br><br>

