  <b>Public transportation directions</b><br>
  We recommend taking public transportation to the Summit to reduce our environmental footprint. The MIT Media Lab is located within a 5-minute walk from the Kendall/MIT stop on the Red Line. For more information about public transportation in the Boston area please visit the <a href="http://www.mbta.com/">MBTA</a> website.<br>
  <ol>
      <li>Take the Red Line to the Kendall/MIT stop.</li>
      <li>Walk straight up Main Street toward Ames St. (past the Kendall Hotel)</li>
      <li>Make a left onto Ames St. (at the corner with the Legal Seafood restaurant).</li>
      <li>The MIT Media Lab is located at the corner of Ames St. and Amherst St.</li>
  </ol><br>

  <b>Driving and Parking</b><br>
  If you must drive to the conference, please refer to the <a href="http://www.media.mit.edu/contact/directions/driving">driving directions</a> and <a href="http://www.media.mit.edu/contact/directions/parking">parking information</a> on the MIT Media Lab website.
